        <p style="color: #666;">
          Designed for endurance in climatic diversity, our systems offer superior thermal efficiency. Double or triple-glazed panels combined with thermally-broken aluminium profiles create a natural barrier against heat loss in winter and heat gain in summer.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
        <%= image_tag("about-10.jpg", alt: "Steady Temperature", class: "w-100") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
